descriptionHtml:
This mod has clearly developed some issues, as such I have removed the download. At the moment I am not playing Skyrim, but somewhere down the line I may try and fix the issues with this mod. If someone else would like to, feel free. 

Apologies for any inconvenience to players of this mod and thank you to everyone that gave feedback.

For those that want it in a more stable but earlier version, Depraved BETA at 

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20296

See my other much more stable 'The Drunkards Drinks' mod at. 

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/16750 

Cheers,
FatalisticZero
